videos.description: UNC's Kenny Williams gets it going early with a sweet stroke from downtown.
videos.headline: Williams drains the corner 3

videos.description: Trevon Duval makes a nice play and finishes on the other end plus the foul for Duke.
videos.headline: Duval gets the steal and score

videos.description: UNC's Joel Berry finds Cameron Johnson streaking down the floor. Grayson Allen attempts to foul to stop the play, but Johnson is too fast and scores the fast-break jam.
videos.headline: Johnson runs the floor and throws it down

videos.description: UNC's Garrison Brooks finishes strong right in the face of Wendell Carter Jr.
videos.headline: Brooks dunks it in Carter's face

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III makes a nice move in the post and finishes with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Bagley throws it down in the paint

videos.description: Grayson Allen makes a great steal and then rises up for the emphatic jam.
videos.headline: Allen shows off the hops

videos.description: Kenny Williams hits another corner three right before the half comes to an end to give UNC a 35-25 lead.
videos.headline: Williams drills a triple before the half

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III and Grayson Allen both put down big dunks for Duke, while Cameron Johnson and Garrison Brooks threw down for North Carolina.
videos.headline: Both UNC and Duke punished the rim in first half

tracking.trackingName: NCB_ SOT FULL Higlight(Both UNC and Duke punished the rim in first half) ESHEET 2018/03/03

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III throws down another powerful two-handed slam early in the second half.
videos.headline: Bagley rocks the rim

videos.description: Trevon Duval finds Marvin Bagley III who throws down a forceful jam for Duke.
videos.headline: Bagley rocks rim off Duval's feed

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets the lay-in to go despite the foul.
videos.headline: Bagley finishes the tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Gary Trent Jr. nails the triple to cap a 9-0 Duke run and give the Blue Devils the lead.
videos.headline: Trent sends the Cameron Crazies into a frenzy

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III rebounds his own miss and throws down another thunderous dunk.
videos.headline: Bagley cleans up his own miss with dunk

videos.description: Theo Pinson takes the contact and still sinks the difficult shot.
videos.headline: Pinson gets the tough shot to go

videos.description: Trevon Duval lobs it up to Marvin Bagley III for the freshman connection that helps solidify Duke's win over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Duval feeds Bagley for monster alley-oop

videos.description: Coach K calls a timeout to bring Grayson Allen off the floor on senior night after a huge 2nd half comeback leads to a Blue Devils victory.
videos.headline: Coach K embraces Allen after curtain call

videos.description: Senior Grayson Allen is at a loss for words after his Blue Devils outscored the Tar Heels by 20 in the 2nd half in his final outing in Cameron Indoor Stadium.
videos.headline: Allen says Duke is 'everything' to him

videos.description: Overcoming a 10-point deficit at halftime, Marvin Bagley III leads No. 5 Duke with 21 points and 15 rebounds in a 74-64 win against No. 9 North Carolina.
videos.headline: Duke rallies to top UNC
